---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Contact
description: Get in touch with Sarah J Mercer.
permalink: /contact/index.html
---

<div class="ahero">
  <div>
    <p class="eyebrow">Contact</p>
    <h1>Say hello.</h1>
    <p>Questions, ideas, things you'd like to see in the series — send them my way. I read every message.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="body-copy">
  <form class="contact-form" name="contact" method="POST" data-netlify="true" netlify-honeypot="bot-field" action="/contact/thanks/">
    <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="contact" />
    <p class="hp"><label>Don't fill this out if you're human: <input name="bot-field" /></label></p>

    <label class="field">
      <span>Your name</span>
      <input type="text" name="name" required />
    </label>

    <label class="field">
      <span>Your email</span>
      <input type="email" name="email" required />
    </label>

    <label class="field">
      <span>Message</span>
      <textarea name="message" rows="6" required></textarea>
    </label>

    <button class="btn" type="submit">Send</button>
  </form>
</div>
